{"tid":970680,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"dc又贏【《蝙蝠俠》延期拍】《水行俠》全球收70億 勢成最賣座DC片","createTime":"2019-01-06T04:49:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T17:53:12.000Z","uid":64922,"like":18,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"966dde98bcea7861fbe0c339ccda2fa3c70c0af7","tid":970680,"uid":64922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:49:24.000Z","msg":"DC超級英雄片《水行俠》（Aquaman）現時全球累積票房達8.876億美元（69.23億港元），成為近年開拍嘅DC宇宙電影最賣座一部，預計本周就可達至9.3億美元（72.53億港元）票房。<br />\n而《水行俠》現於歷年DC漫畫改編電影票房暫排第三，首位係基斯杜化路倫（Christopher Nolan）執導作《蝙蝠俠－夜神起義》（The Dark Knight Rises），於2012年上映錄得嘅10.3億美元（80.3億港元）全球票房成績，隨後係2008年作品《蝙蝠俠&mdash;黑夜之神》（The Dark Knight）嘅10億美元（78億港元）成績，照《水行俠》現時票房走勢，電影定能破10億美元票房成最賣座DC片。<br />\n另外，新一部《蝙蝠俠》電影開拍期將推遲至今年11月，目前劇本已大致完成，要待導演Matt Reeves過目，而之前有傳今次故事會講年輕時期嘅蝙蝠俠，暫未知星班亞弗力（Ben Affleck）會唔會繼續演。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190106/59110151\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59110151&d=ao9E%2F6OdHCl1a577d6iu3dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=d65a5cc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59110151&h=15b7c740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190106/59110151</a><br />\n<br />\n年青版batman睇來賓佬實比人飛硬"},{"pid":"e8ea6277ab535ab7b3d951ea1a1055ca7beb6739","tid":970680,"uid":41394,"like":36,"dislike":196,"score":-160,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"睇完水行俠 勁伏 依為自己睇緊超人迪加"},{"pid":"0042fc05ce18eb93063747aa8bfe8a5e56a70aa2","tid":970680,"uid":52215,"like":169,"dislike":24,"score":145,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T04:56:35.000Z","msg":"aquaman 海底世界真係屌打好多超英戲設定"},{"pid":"623b1a62e15827466c26ee2041b5d8a4ebb9dff4","tid":970680,"uid":64922,"like":2,"dislike":45,"score":-43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:10:12.000Z","msg":"講下Nicole Kidman都幾有運<